## Key Implementation Notes

- Chip height is `h-7` (28px) to fit within the `h-9` (36px) header with vertical centering.
- Color dot uses `motion.span` with `animate={{ backgroundColor: visual.color }}` for smooth color transitions when switching agents.
- Streaming pulse animates opacity `[1, 0.4, 1]` over 1.5s with infinite repeat. When NOT streaming, opacity is just `1` with a 0.3s easeOut transition for the color change.
- No-agent dot uses `border border-dashed border-muted-foreground/40` with no background fill.
- Name truncation at `max-w-[160px]` with `truncate` class. The tooltip shows full name context ("Agent settings").
- Agent name transition uses `AnimatePresence mode="wait"` keyed on `agent?.id ?? 'no-agent'`. The initial state slides from above (y: -3), exit slides down (y: 3), duration 0.12s.
- `whileTap={{ scale: 0.97 }}` for press feedback.
- Click handler calls `setAgentDialogOpen(true)` from `useAppStore`.
- Accessibility: `aria-label` is `"${agent.name} — agent settings"` when agent exists, `"Configure agent"` when null. Dot and chevron are `aria-hidden`.

